A handy script to watch your files and run a command in the background.

INSTALLATION
============
bundle install
tail -2 Gemfile >> /your/app/Gemfile
cp watch/watch.rb /your/app
cd /your/app

USAGE
=====
# The default assumes that you have RSpec tests in /your/app/spec
#  If you want to change the test command, then edit watch.rb.
#  Change line 3: command = 'rspec spec' to however you run your
#  tests.

ruby watch.rb

